title: REESE Towpower 72783 Coupler Lock, Adjustable Storage Security, Heavy-Duty Steel, Yellow and Chrome
description: This REESE Towpower universal coupler lock prevents theft and keeps your trailer secure. The bright, yellow color is highly visible and deters thieves. It features a ratchet design with six locking positions for versatility, and is designed to fit 1-7/8 In., 2 In., and 2-5/16 In. couplers.
